      "content": "Self-treating worsening shortness of breath with intensive breathing routines or extra antihistamines carries significant risks, as the cause could be anything from poorly controlled asthma to another respiratory issue. Asthma management requires professional diagnosis to determine if the issue is related to inflammation, triggers, or medication effectiveness. Since your symptoms are impacting simple daily tasks, please prioritize speaking with a healthcare provider to ensure your safety and get an accurate diagnosis.",
      "source": "target",
